                    </article>

                                                                                                </div>
                        

                        <p>Korstad said that he thinks DSWS will take encouragement from the raise increase, and said&nbsp;peaceful protests often bring attention to issues and put pressure on people who make policies. </p>
<p>The increase might “put things off for a while,”&nbsp;Arcidiacono&nbsp;noted, adding that&nbsp;minimum wage is always increasing and&nbsp;the issue may come up again.  </p>
